[
  {
    "text": "日々の暮らしの織物",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.10166607057451951,
      "left": 0.3235293982843137,
      "width": 0.35294117941176395,
      "height": 0.030303029040404043
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "朝の日差しが静かな通りを優しく照らし、温かな光が木々の間を通り抜けて地面に美し",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.16446939418877496,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7647058887254881,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "い影を落としています。鳥たちが木の上で優しく歌い、その心地よいさえずりが眠って",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.1871966659690781,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.758823441176473,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "いた街を目覚めさせ、新しい一",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2099239377493811,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.27450980620914983,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "日が希望と可能性に満ちた始まりを迎えます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2099239377493811,
      "left": 0.39215686013071843,
      "width": 0.40980391625816925,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "技術の進歩は前例のないスピードで私たちの生活様式と働き方を根本的に変えていま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2449618150773482,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.741764714681371,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "す。人工知能から再生可能エネルギーまで、毎",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2676890868576512,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.40901960979575075,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "日新しい革新と発明",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2676890868576512,
      "left": 0.5266666637173195,
      "width": 0.17647058970588195,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "が現れ、これらの技",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2676890868576512,
      "left": 0.7031372534232013,
      "width": 0.17647058970588175,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "術的進歩は社会のあらゆる側面に深い影響を与え、私たちが世界と関わる方法を再構築",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29041635863795434,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7647058887254881,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "しています。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3131436304182573,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.11450978456699408,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "古代文明は驚くべき記念碑と建築の奇跡を建設し、これらの壮大な構造物は何千年もの",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.34912847740373704,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7631371934477134,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "時を経ても堂々と立ち続けています。エジプトのピラミッドから中国の万里の長",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3718557491840401,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7039215667483648,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "城ま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3718557491840401,
      "left": 0.8215686206699334,
      "width": 0.039215686601306796,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "で、これらの建築物は先祖の卓越した知恵と驚くべき創",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3945830209643431,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.48784309732026215,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "造性を示すだけでなく、人類文",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3945830209643431,
      "left": 0.6054901512418309,
      "width": 0.2745097586601319,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "明の輝かしい歴史の証人でもあります。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4173102927446461,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3509803662581704,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "教育は社会の進歩と個人の成長",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4523481700726133,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.27450980620914983,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を推進する根本的な基礎です。体系的な学習と継続的な",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4523481700726133,
      "left": 0.3921568601307185,
      "width": 0.48823529166666557,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "知識の蓄積を通じて、人々は自分たちの生活と周囲のコミュニティを改善するために必",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4750754418529163,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7633333186846395,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "要な様々な道具、技能、そして深い洞察を獲得し、より良い未来の構築に貢献すること",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4978027136332194,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.763529370882353,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ができます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5205299854135224,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.11568626331699373,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "自",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5555678627414895,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.01960784330065356,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "然は比類のない美しい景観と生命を維持するために不可欠な貴重な資源を惜しみなく",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5555678627414895,
      "left": 0.13725489722222217,
      "width": 0.7450980454248346,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "提供してくれます。清らかな空気から純粋な水、肥沃な土壌から多様な生物まで、環境",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5782951345217926,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7594117322058822,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を保護し大切にすることは、私たちの世代の責任であり、未来の子孫が地球の素晴らし",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6010224063020956,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7647058887254884,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "さを享受し続けるための鍵となります。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6237496780823987,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3503921224101316,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "効果的なコミュニケーションは異なる文",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6597345250678786,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176395,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "化",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6597345250678786,
      "left": 0.4705882333333326,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "、民族、国家の間に理解と協力の重要な橋を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6597345250678786,
      "left": 0.49019607663398623,
      "width": 0.3921568660130704,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "架けます。言語は人類の最も偉大な発明の一つとして、地理的・文",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6824617968481815,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.5843136940359479,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的な境界を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6824617968481815,
      "left": 0.72156859125817,
      "width": 0.0980392165032676,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "化",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6824617968481815,
      "left": 0.7019607479575165,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "越え",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6824617968481815,
      "left": 0.8196078077614375,
      "width": 0.03921568660130698,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "て、お互いの考え、経験、知恵",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7051890686284845,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2737254922712413,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7051890686284845,
      "left": 0.39137254619281,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "共有することを可能にし、相互理解、尊重、信頼の関",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7051890686284845,
      "left": 0.4109803894934636,
      "width": 0.47058819901960786,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "係を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7279163404087875,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.03921568660130712,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "築くことができます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7279163404087875,
      "left": 0.15686274052287574,
      "width": 0.19411762573529465,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "科学研究は厳密な方法と絶え間ない探求を通じて、宇宙に隠された謎と法則を徐々に明",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7629542177367548,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7639215412091496,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "らかにしています。それぞれの新しい発見は未知の世界への扉を開くようなものであ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7856814895170577,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7419607764379074,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "り、同時により多くの魅力的な問題をもたらし、科学者たちがさらに広大な未知の領域",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8084087612973607,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7641176600735272,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を探求し続ける動機となっています。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8311360330776639,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.32921567231209153,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "芸術はその独特な方法で、言葉の制限を超えた深い感情と抽象的な思想を表現し伝えま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8661739104056311,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7639215399836593,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "す。絵画、音楽、彫刻、文学など、これらの創",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8889011821859341,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.4098039166258166,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
